
---

## **Quick Start Commands**

To create this entire project structure quickly:

```bash
# Create project
mkdir task-management-tool && cd task-management-tool

# Initialize git
git init

# Create directory structure
mkdir -p client/src/{components/{auth,boards,cards,lists,common},hooks,store,utils,types} server/src/{models,controllers,routes,middleware,utils} .github/workflows

# Copy all the files above into their respective locations

# Install dependencies
cd client && npm install
cd ../server && npm install

# Start development
docker-compose up -d
# OR
cd server && npm run dev
cd client && npm start
